column5: AIMT Regardless of market in general all this fiddlefucking around under 20 makes it just too tempting for the shorts to drive it to new lows With no volume it would take very little effort to do so I just hope we can finally put in a decent reversal once it happens Chart is just so obviouslower highs lower lows and lower volume Short sellers dream

AIMT This whole Mexican tarried stuff is just to distract from Muellers statement Trump has a list of these outrages and they pull one out when they need itNot wanting to start a political argument Just saying this will likely blow over soon
